subject: Rugby (Game)
lead_paragraph: France ousted the favorite New Zealand, 20-18, and England upset Australia, 12-10, to advance to the World Cup semifinals. France, the host country, and England will play Saturday at the Stade de France near Paris. The other quarterfinals are today, with South Africa playing Fiji and Argentina playing Scotland.
